### Utilities ###

initializer_list

include directive:
    #include <initializer_list>

object of type std::initializer_list is proxy object that provides acces to array of objects
Some states std::initializer_list will create automatically constructed

initializer_list

cap:
    size -> returns the number of elements in the initializer list

